{"tid":1022197,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴郡吸納Red Hat 減持蘋果","createTime":"2019-02-14T23:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T00:12:44.000Z","uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0abee022b8b04994984d6612861279099c9bdcc6","tid":1022197,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T23:59:20.000Z","msg":"股神畢非德的投資旗艦巴郡公布季度股票組合變動細節，較囑目的是購入軟件商Red Hat股份及減持蘋果公司股份。<br />\n<br />\n根據公告，巴郡在上季內吸納了417.5萬股Red Hat，市值相當於7.33億美元。同時，集團吸納加拿大能源公司Suncor的1075萬股，以及巴西網上付款營運企業StoneCo的1416萬股。<br />\n<br />\n另外，巴郡減持289萬股蘋果，令到其持股量降低約1%，仍有2.49億股，市值相當於394億美元。同時，巴郡減持能源公司Phillips 66股份約22%，即接近350萬股；另沽出聯合航空(United Airlines)約15%持股，折合400萬股。該公司又沽清尚持有的4100萬股甲骨文(Oracle)。"},{"pid":"05fb89421d6531f7769bf209f71dd5b8716d44d6","tid":1022197,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T00:01:49.000Z","msg":"John Linux <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5997d4f81b4afb09e96e1fe26fcedc81c3d00522","tid":1022197,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"好少啫 1%？係咪？"},{"pid":"a948f1558a7c9c46611364da3364a28e34d49122","tid":1022197,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5997d4f81b4afb09e96e1fe26fcedc81c3d00522","tid":1022197,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"好少啫 1%？係咪？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T00:12:44.000Z","msg":"仍有2.49億股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}